Intent: Ensure a class only has one instance, and provide a global point of access to it.
确保一个类只有一个实例，并提供一个接入点来访问这个实例
Applicability: Use the Singleton pattern when

there must be exactly one instance of a class, and it must be accessible to clients from a well-known access point
必须只有一个类的实例
when the sole instance should be extensible by subclassing, 
这个实例必须在被子类继承的时候可以通过一个接口访问到
and clients should be able to use an extended instance without modifying their code
应用程序可以不用修饰自己的代码就能应用一个扩展实例

Typical Use Case:

the logging class
日志类
managing a connection to a database
管理一个数据库链接
file manager
文件管理器